Theme/Base V3 1.1.0

	* [Bug] Fix the rigid width issue for listing tables that came from bourbon.
	* Retool how widgets areas work to allow page-level templates to be specified and managed.
	* Switch the View debugging information to use the standard UI structure for collapsible fieldsets as
	  of base-v3.
	* New collapsible fieldset legend support with chevron hints.
	* Colour tweaks for messages.
	* Edit repository functionality and additional stats on remote repos on the updater system.
	* Minor text changes only.
